snippet.title: Smoop Can't Sleep! AVAILABLE NOW!!
snippet.description: Smoop Can't Sleep! is a short, difficult, intense 2d platformer-shooter where you play as the titular Smoop, whose long sleep has been rudely interrupted by unexpected intruders.
